description: We serve Coastal Carolina Cuisine and all American favorites.  Our key dish is smooth and tasty cheesy grits served alongside chicken and fried shrimp Po Boy sandwiches or shrimp & grits.   Our sides are seasonal and include salads, cucumbers and onions, fries, mac & cheese and hoppin john.  For dessert we make our own chocolate covered bananas.For catering we add fresh made fried chicken tenders, full breakfast menus and anything else you can think of. We will work with you to create a menu that works for you makes your event a success.We cook on our truck using fresh ingredients.
name: Red Plate Blue Plate Truck
